high_descs: Turn left, hang a left just past the couch, turn left at the chair and turn to the right just beyond the table to face the couch.
Close the lid to the laptop computer behind the red card near the back of the couch and pick it up.
Turn around, hang a left at the wall and walk to the ottoman near the chair.
Place the laptop computer on the right side of the ottoman.
Turn around, hang a right at the fireplace, and walk to the couch.
Close the lid to the laptop computer to the left of the red card and pick it up.
Turn around, hang a left at the wall and walk to the ottoman near the chair.
Place the laptop on the left side of the ottoman near the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place two laptop computers on the ottoman.

high_descs: Turn left, cross the room, walk to white table, turn right, walk to front of couch, turn right, walk to end of couch, turn right to face couch cushion with laptops on it.
Pick up laptop closer to the back of the couch.
Turn left, walk past table, turn left, walk to ottoman.
Put the laptop on the right side of the ottoman, oriented horizontally.
Turn left, walk past table, turn right, walk to couch.
Pick up laptop from the couch.
Turn left, walk past table, turn left, walk to ottoman.
Put the laptop on the ottoman to the left of the other laptop, perpendicular to it..
cross the room to the opposite corner of the couch in front of you, stopping when facing the two laptops
close and take the rear laptop
cross the room to the chair with the ottoman
put the laptop on the right-side of the ottoman
cross the room back to the couch cushion with the laptop
close and take the laptop from the couch cushion
cross the room back to the ottoman with the other laptop
put the laptop to the left of the other laptop on the ottoman
anns.task_desc: place two laptops on the ottoman

high_descs: Go around the blue sofa to its front.
Close the black laptop further back and pick it up.
Turn around to go to the arm chair with foot rest.
Place the laptop on the foot rest.
Turn around and go back to the blue sofa.
Close and pick up the other laptop on the sofa.
Turn around to go back to the arm chair.
Place the laptop on the foot rest next to the other laptop.
anns.task_desc: Move the laptops from the sofa to the foot rest.

high_descs: Turn left to face the wall, walk until reach the end of the couch, turn right, walk to the ottoman, turn right.  Walk along the couch until the last section where two laptops and a credit card are placed.
Close the laptop that is farther away from you, closest to the red blanket.  Pick it up.
Turn around, walk to the wall, turn left towards the chair and ottoman.
Place the laptop on the right side of the ottoman, with the opening facing the wall.
Turn around, walk to the fireplace, turn right towards the couch, walk to the couch.
Close the laptop in front of you and pick it up.
Turn around, walk to the wall, turn left and walk to the ottoman.
Place the laptop on the left side of the ottoman, next to the other one, with the opening end facing you.
anns.task_desc: Close and move both laptops from the couch to the ottoman.
